import React, { useState } from 'react'

import { Card, Button } from 'react-bootstrap'
import 'bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css'

import './css/Vhe.scss'

const Vhe = (props) => {
    const [isOpen, setIsOpen] = useState(false)
    return (
        <>
            <Card className='vhe_CARD' style={{ width: '18rem' }}>
                <Card.Img variant="top" src={props.vhe.vheImageUrl}/>
                <Card.Body>
                    <Card.Title>{props.vhe.vheId}</Card.Title>
                    <Card.Text style={{display: isOpen ? 'block' : 'none'}}>
                        Coliving: {props.vhe.colivingAllowed}
                    </Card.Text>
                    <Card.Text style={{display: isOpen ? 'block' : 'none'}}>
                        Stay duration: {props.vhe.stayDuration}
                    </Card.Text>
                    <Card.Text style={{display: isOpen ? 'block' : 'none'}}>
                        Max stay duration: {props.vhe.maxStayDuration}
                    </Card.Text>
                    <Card.Text style={{display: isOpen ? 'block' : 'none'}}>
                        SNF certificate: {props.vhe.snfCertificateApproved}
                    </Card.Text>
                    <Card.Text style={{display: isOpen ? 'block' : 'none'}}>
                        SNF certificate location: {props.vhe.snfCertificateLocation}
                    </Card.Text>
                    <Card.Text style={{display: isOpen ? 'block' : 'none'}}>
                        AKF certificate: {props.vhe.akfCertificateApproved}
                    </Card.Text>
                    <Card.Text style={{display: isOpen ? 'block' : 'none'}}>
                        AKF certificate location: {props.vhe.akfCertificateLocation}
                    </Card.Text>
                    <Card.Text style={{display: isOpen ? 'block' : 'none'}}>
                        Changeover time: {props.vhe.changeoverTime}
                    </Card.Text>
                    <Card.Text style={{display: isOpen ? 'block' : 'none'}}>
                        House rules location: {props.vhe.houseRulesLocation}
                    </Card.Text>
                    <Button
                        variant="primary"
                        onClick={() => setIsOpen(!isOpen)}
                    >
                        VHE details
                    </Button>
                </Card.Body>
            </Card>
        </>
    )
}

export default Vhe
